author: gsim
msg: Temporary fix to issue that results in an assertion from Dispatcher.cpp. Where an interest in write is signalled just as a readable event is triggered it is possible for a writeable (or read-writeable) event to be triggered before the earlier event is processed. This change ensures they are processed serially by queueing them up for the first thread to handle.
